            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1646738572350-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are in the oven, cut your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander & parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
