    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> parsley</strong>, <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> (not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!) with your<strong> dried oregano</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 1/2 tbsp] </span>[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>chimichurri</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1646738591011-x200.jpg",
