    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak </strong>and wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and <strong>roasted veg</strong> to a plate with the <strong>sliced steak </strong>to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>rocket </strong>and a <strong>fried egg </strong>and drizzle the<strong> chimichurri</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
